Actions.Text: REFERRED TO COMMERCE, ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT AND SMALL BUSINESS

Title: Requires the empire state development corporation to conduct a study on the economic impact of the Labor Day Parade (West Indian Carnival)
Summary: Requires the empire state development corporation to conduct a study on the economic impact of the Labor Day Parade (West Indian Carnival) and submit a report to the governor and the legislature on its findings.
ActClause: AN ACT requiring the empire state development corporation to conduct a study on the economic impact of the Labor Day Parade (West Indian Carnival)
